<subSubSection pageId="null" pageNumber="210" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
Ausdauernd; 20-50 cm hoch; 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">kahl</emphasis>
(
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
auch im 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
)
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken originalValue="bläulich" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">blaeulich</normalizedToken>
, flach.
</emphasis>
Kelch mit kurzen, lanzettlichen Zipfeln. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Krone 0,8</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">1 cm lang</emphasis>
(ohne Sporn), 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
leuchtend zitronengelb, mit orangegelbem Gaumen; Sporn etwa so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken originalValue="übrige" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">uebrige</normalizedToken>
Krone. Frucht 4
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">5 mm lang.</emphasis>
Sonst wie 
<taxonomicName class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" genus="Linaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="null" pageNumber="210" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<authorityName pageId="null" pageNumber="210">L.</authorityName>
vulgaris
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 8). - 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, montan, seltener subalpin. Trockene, lockere, steinige, meist kalkarme 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Felssteppen, Getreidefelder, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Gebüsche" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Gebuesche</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<pageBreakToken pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Verbreitung</pageBreakToken>
. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<normalizedToken originalValue="südlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">suedlich</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
): 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Ostpyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Ostpyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
, Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Südkarpaten" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Suedkarpaten</normalizedToken>
. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen (?), Wallis, Aostatal, Langenseegebiet (Lavena), 
<normalizedToken originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin und angrenzende italienische Gebiete, Comerseegebiet, Veltlin, Puschlav (?), Gebiet von Bormio, Bergamasker Alpen (Val Brembana, Valle Seriana, Valle di Scalve), Vintschgau, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Münstertal" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Muenstertal</normalizedToken>
; nicht 
<normalizedToken originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Nach 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Valdès" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Valdes</normalizedToken>
(1970) 
<normalizedToken originalValue="müßte" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">muesste</normalizedToken>
die Art 
<taxonomicName authority="(Lam.) Valdes" authorityName="Valdes" baseAuthorityName="Lam." class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" genus="Linaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="null" pageNumber="210" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pallidiflora">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">
<authorityName pageId="null" pageNumber="210">L.</authorityName>
pallidiflora
</emphasis>
(Lam.) 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Valdès" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">Valdes</normalizedToken>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="heißen" pageId="null" pageNumber="210">heissen</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
